All Classes

  • Class Description
    Access
    Contains generic methods for accessing data in the database.
    ApiHandler
    A default handler for web API requests.
    ApiRequest
    A generic API request.
    ApiResult
    A generic result of an API request.
    AuthToken
    Represents an authorization token assigned to a user of the family map.
    AuthTokenAccess
    Contains methods for accessing authorization token data in the database.
    ClearHandler
    Handler used to receive POST requests to clear all data from the database.
    ClearResult
    The result of a request to the /clear API route.
    ClearService
    Contains methods providing functionality of the /clear API route.
    Database
    Stores a connection to the database.
    DBException
    An exception caused by database operations.
    DefaultHandler
    Handler used to serve up a static web site for interacting with the server.
    Event
    Represents an event occurring in one person's life.
    EventAccess
    Contains methods for accessing event data in the database.
    EventHandler
    Handler used to receive GET requests to get Event data from the database.
    EventRequest
    A request to the /event/[eventId] route.
    EventResult
    The result of a request to the /event/[eventID] API route.
    EventService
    Contains methods providing functionality of the /event API route.
    EventsResult
    The result of a request to the /event route.
    FillHandler
    Handler used to receive POST requests to generate data for a user.
    FillRequest
    A request to the /fill route.
    FillResult
    The result of a request to the /fill route.
    FillService
    Contains methods providing functionality of the /fill API route.
    Gender
    Provides constants representing options for a person's or user's gender.
    LoadHandler
    Handler used to receive POST requests to load data into the database.
    LoadRequest
    A request to the /load route.
    LoadResult
    The result of a request to the /load route.
    LoadService
    Contains methods providing functionality of the /load API route.
    LocationGenerator
    Provides methods to generate random locations.
    LoginHandler
    Handler used to receive POST requests to log a user in.
    LoginRequest
    A request to the /user/login route.
    LoginResult
    The result of a request to the /user/login or /user/register route.
    LoginService
    Contains methods providing functionality of the /user/login API route.
    NameGenerator
    Provides methods to generate random names.
    ObjectEncoder
    Provides methods to serialize objects and deserialize strings/streams.
    Person
    Represents a person and his/her relationships in the family map.
    PersonAccess
    Contains methods for accessing person data in the database.
    PersonHandler
    Handler used to receive GET requests to get Person data from the database.
    PersonRequest
    A request to the /person/[personId] route.
    PersonResult
    The result of a request to the /person/[personID] API route.
    PersonService
    Contains methods providing functionality of the /person API route.
    PersonsResult
    The result of a request to the /person API route.
    RegisterHandler
    Handler used to receive POST requests to register a new user.
    RegisterRequest
    A request to the /user/register route.
    RegisterService
    Contains methods providing functionality of the /user/register API route.
    Server
    Main class of the server used to set up routes and listen.
    User
    Represents a user of the family map application.
    UserAccess
    Contains methods for accessing user data in the database.
